data.description: Welcome to this Beautiful two story home.  This home offers 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths of living space. The open floor plan offers living/dining combo, kitchen features a gas stove, lots of counter-space, a spacious corner pantry, and an island great for entertaining.  The floor plan includes an upstairs space perfect for a home office/game room area or an extra living space.  All bedrooms located on second level.  Primary bedroom and bath are located on second level. Large and spacious backyard.  Very well maintained home that was built in 2020.  Wiring for security system, water softener (leased).  Easy access to I35, 10 minutes from the forum for shopping, restaurants, entertainment. Only 10 minute drive to Randolph Air Force Base. Access to neighborhood amenities with pool, playground, sports court.  Ready to Move in NOW! Schedule your showing today and don't miss this opportunity.
